               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; name of the protagonist; names of the donors; incipit of Text I; incipit of Text II; note in the upper margin (fol. 4r); elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.&#xD;
In the incipit page of Text II (fols. 3r), a few lines are rubricated (alternating with black lines)</rubric>
